    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is sound with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use on the driver's seat bolster, and all electronics are fully functional. The exterior presents well, though you may find a few small stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches that are common for a car of this age. It serves as a dependable and comfortable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 34000.0,
