    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still got that crisp, clean feel inside and out. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and has been super reliable. I\u2019m really looking for a good home for it, so if you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
