    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring mechanical harmony and precise power delivery. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity, and the suspension remains factory-tight with no bushing deflection. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the Nappa leather interior shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine with a documented service history and no mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
